Raw: The meeting on Monday at the Knightsbridge Hall , at 3.15 p.m. , will be addressed by the Lady Isabel Hampden Margesson and Miss Marie Naylor . The chair will be taken by Mrs. Mansel . These meetings are for women only ; no men will be admitted .
